    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="01-helloworld程序源代码的编写以及源码解析"><a href="#01-helloworld程序源代码的编写以及源码解析" class="headerlink" title="01_helloworld程序源代码的编写以及源码解析"></a>01_helloworld程序源代码的编写以及源码解析</h1><h3 id="【1】源代码："><a href="#【1】源代码：" class="headerlink" title="【1】源代码："></a>【1】源代码：</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello world!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    getchar();</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="【2】源码解析："><a href="#【2】源码解析：" class="headerlink" title="【2】源码解析："></a>【2】源码解析：</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 导入（包含）一个文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// stdio.h是标准库 i =&gt; input  o =&gt; output 标准输入输出库</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// .h表示该文件是头文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &lt;&gt;表示导入系统文件 &quot;&quot;表示导入自定义文件</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment">// int 数据类型 整型 如果出现在函数前表示函数的返回值</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment">// main 程序的主函数，是程序的入口 程序有且仅有一个主函数 </span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment">// ()里面表示函数的参数 函数的参数可以有多个 中间用&quot;,&quot;分割</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123; <span class="comment">// &#123;&#125; 表示函数体 代码体 程序体</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello world!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// printf()是系统提供的stdio.h头文件中提供的函数 表示在标准输入输出设备上打印字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// &quot;&quot;中的内容称为字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// &quot;;&quot;表示一条语句的结束</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    getchar();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 这是带阻塞的代码，用于解决程序的运行结果(终端窗口)一闪而过</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 作用是获取用户输入的一个字符</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// return 如果出现在其他函数中表示该函数结束；如果出现在main函数中表示该程序结束</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 0 表示该函数的返回值 函数的返回值要和函数的返回值类型对应</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 两个正斜杠表示行注释 只能注释一行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">这是一行块注释</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">可以注释多行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">注释内容不参与程序编译</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="system函数的简单介绍以及使用"><a href="#system函数的简单介绍以及使用" class="headerlink" title="system函数的简单介绍以及使用"></a>system函数的简单介绍以及使用</h1><h3 id="【1】介绍："><a href="#【1】介绍：" class="headerlink" title="【1】介绍："></a>【1】介绍：</h3><h5 id="头文件："><a href="#头文件：" class="headerlink" title="头文件："></a>头文件：</h5><ul><li>要使用该函数，需要包含头文件stdlib.h</li></ul><h5 id="功能："><a href="#功能：" class="headerlink" title="功能："></a>功能：</h5><ul><li>system()可以打开一个外部的应用程序</li></ul><h5 id="返回值："><a href="#返回值：" class="headerlink" title="返回值："></a>返回值：</h5><ul><li>当函数正常执行完毕返回int类型的数字0</li><li>但函数执行出现错误或执行失败返回其他Int类型数字</li></ul><h3 id="【3】代码演示："><a href="#【3】代码演示：" class="headerlink" title="【3】代码演示："></a>【3】代码演示：</h3><h4 id="打开软件："><a href="#打开软件：" class="headerlink" title="打开软件："></a>打开软件：</h4><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    system(<span class="string">&quot;calc&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 打开计算器</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="获取并打印输出函数的返回值："><a href="#获取并打印输出函数的返回值：" class="headerlink" title="获取并打印输出函数的返回值："></a>获取并打印输出函数的返回值：</h4><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt; // 注意本程序要调用printf()，要包含头文件stdio.h</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main02</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> value;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    value = system(<span class="string">&quot;calc&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, value);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// %d是一个占位符，表示在某个位置输出一个整型数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    getchar();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="【4】注意事项："><a href="#【4】注意事项：" class="headerlink" title="【4】注意事项："></a>【4】注意事项：</h3><ul><li><p>如果打开的程序带路径，需要使用”\\&quot;或”/“</p><p>如：<code>system(&quot;C:\\calc&quot;)</code>或<code>system(&quot;C:/calc&quot;)</code></p><p>以上路径是我随意写的，该路径很大可能是错误的！不要将其写进你的代码！！！</p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
